{"tw": {"4071430": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "女冒險者的調教術", "steam_appid": 4071430, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071430/extras/442a83bb3aceb6514101aaf27d0ab68d.avif?t=1770173776\" width=780 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一個被債務壓得喘不過氣的女孩，已經沒辦法再靠自己的魅力去借到錢了。好在債主看你實在慘，心軟了一下。發現你本身就是個冒險者後，乾脆給你指了條活路：去當馴獸師吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >於是你只能一頭栽進地牢，捕捉並馴服各種怪物，再把它們賣掉換錢，目標只有一個：把債務還清！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071430/extras/3d537c6e255c60066b48b006aa42a114.avif?t=1770173776\" width=780 height=111 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >女冒險者的調教術是一款帶點平台跳躍要素的橫版地牢探索遊戲。你需要進入不同類型的地牢，與各種生物戰鬥，將它們捕獲、訓練，並出售來賺取利潤。你能不能找到那些極其稀有的怪物呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在時間耗盡之前完成一切，成功還清你的債務！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071430/extras/6c51122f56430b44dd12a3b0be24fe45.avif?t=1770173776\" width=780 height=770 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071430/extras/061a6c2ec15a679c609add291a3d7e00.avif?t=1770173776\" width=780 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多個關卡，每個關卡都有獨特的設計</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩法輕鬆有趣，上手非常快</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >任務板上可以接取特殊的支線任務</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲中存在可收集的稀有敵人</p></li></ul>", "about_the_game": "<p cl