u can no longer rely on your charm to borrow more money. Fortunately, a dept creditor takes pity on your situation. Seeing that you are also an adventurer, they suggest an alternative path: become a Tamer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now you must venture into the dungeon to capture and tame creatures, selling them for profit in order to pay off your debt!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071430/extras/6a8a33f7c8161824c385e3f505a2498c.avif?t=1770173776\" width=780 height=111 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tame Me Hard is a side-scrolling dungeon crawler with a touch of platforming. Venture into different types of dungeons to encounter a variety of creatures to fight, capture, train, and sell for profit. Will you be able to find even the rarest of them?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do it all before time runs out and clear your debt!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071430/extras/a7d2b443cd4787f0c8da1909e6f78751.avif?t=1770173776\" width=780 height=770 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071430/extras/5a7d53502689e9185f143f5a6d5fabdf.avif?t=1770173776\" width=780 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple levels</strong> with their own distinct design</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fun and simple gameplay</strong>, that takes no time to learn</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Special subquests</strong> available on the Quest Board</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rare enemies</strong> to collect!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071430/extras/b5328f03a669359db416d466e4a4d2a5.avif?t=1770173776\" width=780 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a girl burdened by debt. You can no longer rely on your charm to borrow more money. Fortunately, a dept creditor takes pity on your situation. Seeing that you are also an adventurer, they suggest an alternative path: become a Tamer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now you must venture into the dungeon to capture and tame creatures, selling them for profit in order to pay off your debt!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071430/extras/6a8a33f7c8161824c385e3f505a2498c.avif?t=1770173776\" width=780 height=111 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tame Me Hard is a side-scrolling dungeon crawler with a touch of platforming. Venture into different types of dungeons to encounter a variety of creatures to fight, capture, train, and sell for profit. Will you be able to find even the rarest of them?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do it all before time runs out and clear your debt!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071430/extras/a7d2b443cd4787f0c8da1909e6f78751.avif?t=1770173776\" width=780 height=770 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4071430/extras/5a7d53502689e9185f143f5a6d5fabdf.avif?t=1770173776\" width=780 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></